Rest of NBA Preseason May Be Canceled, Players Union’s Derek Fisher Says

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-10-04T22:00:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/rest-of-nba-preseason-may-be-canceled-players-union-s-derek-fisher-says.html
The rest of the National Basketball
Association preseason is at risk after owners and players could
not reach agreement on a new collective bargaining agreement
today.  “We anticiapte coming out of today with the reality that
the rest of the preseason will probably be canceled some time
soon,”  Derek Fisher , president of the NBA’s players union said
at a news conference, adding that the start of the regular
season also could be wiped out.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  